{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, integrating THz into ISAC, i.e., THz-ISAC, is envisioned to enable the emerging applications with both ultra-high communication rates and ultra-accurate sensing requirements, such as V2X and human-computer interaction.",
    "Nevertheless, operating at a very high carrier frequency, THz-ISAC suffers from the challenges of limited coverage range and severe pathloss, and is vulnerable to LoS blockage.",
    "The extremely large antenna arrays with high beamforming gain can be utilized to compensate for the severe pathloss and the IRS can enlarge the coverage of THz-ISAC by introducing the virtual LoS links.",
    "Moreover, the flexible configurations of extremely large antenna arrays and IRS can be facilitated by AI, making it a promising candidate for THz-ISAC.",
    "Liu et al. [253] studied the system capacity maximization problem for IRS-aided THz-ISAC systems."
  ]
}